# PlatinumRx Assignment

## 📌 Objective

This project demonstrates core Data Analyst skills including:

* SQL (database design and querying)
* Excel (data analysis and reporting)
* Python (basic programming logic)

---

## 📂 Project Structure

Data_Analyst_Assignment/

│

├── SQL/

│   ├── 01_Hotel_Schema_Setup.sql

│   ├── 02_Hotel_Queries.sql

│   ├── 03_Clinic_Schema_Setup.sql

│   └── 04_Clinic_Queries.sql

│

├── Spreadsheets/

│   └── Ticket_Analysis.xlsx

│

├── Python/

│   ├── 01_Time_Converter.py

│   └── 02_Remove_Duplicates.py

---

## 🧠 SQL Tasks

### Hotel Management System

* Retrieved last booked room per user
* Calculated total billing amounts
* Filtered high-value bills
* Identified most and least ordered items
* Found second highest billing customers

### Clinic Management System

* Calculated revenue by sales channel
* Identified top customers
* Computed monthly profit/loss
* Found most and least profitable clinics

---

## 📊 Spreadsheet Tasks

* Used **INDEX-MATCH** to populate missing values
* Created helper columns for:

  * Same Day comparison
  * Same Hour comparison
* Used **Pivot Table** for outlet-wise analysis

---

## 🐍 Python Tasks

### 1. Time Converter

* Converted minutes into hours and minutes format

### 2. Remove Duplicates

* Removed duplicate characters from a string using loops

